This tool is developed for testing SPI on ADLINK px30

It can be used elsewhere also if we have spi device entry and w25q64 SPI fixure.

Building:
	To build this binaries
		make

Usage:
	adlink_spi_tool <mraa spi bus no>

E.g.
	sudo adlink_spi_tool 0
here,

	0 is MRAA SPI bus no
it will show menu remaing option.
